      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it still has that amazing 'new car' feel inside and out. No scratches, no dents, just pure driving bliss. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner super happy. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
