    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of the 997.1 Carrera S, maintained to a concours standard. This specimen features the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power across the entire rev range. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers surgical precision, complemented by a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach: the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) provides impeccable damping, while the undercarriage remains dry with no evidence of seepage from the rear main seal. Recent spectroscopic oil analysis confirms engine health, and the Bore Scoring inspection yielded zero concerns. Finished in original paint with consistent micron readings across all panels, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
