    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector-grade example that must be seen to be appreciated. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, having been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating since its first week on the road. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the original factory scent is still remarkably present. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the dashboard is entirely free of sun damage or hairline cracks. Mechanically, this car has been over-maintained, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of service records exclusively from certified master technicians. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never been driven in inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle that has been preserved with meticulous, enthusiast-level care.",
